  "title": "ISic003701. Epitaph of Martirios",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησεν</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μαρτίριος\"><span data-text=\"Μαρτίριος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Μαρτύριος\">Μαρτίριος</span></span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"εἴκοσι\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"εἴκοσι\">εἴκοσι</span>  <span data-text=\"δύω\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"δύω\">δύω</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"εἰρήνη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"εἰρήνη\">εἰρήνη</span>  <span data-text=\"σοι\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"σύ\">σοι</span>  <span data-text=\"☧Χριστός\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">(Χριστό)ς</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ἔζησεν</span>  <span data-text=\"Μαρτίριος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Μαρτύριος\">Μαρτίριος</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"εἴκοσι\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"εἴκοσι\">εἴκοσι</span>  <span data-text=\"δύω\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"δύω\">δύω</span>  <span data-text=\"εἰρήνη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"εἰρήνη\">εἰρήνη</span>  <span data-text=\"σοι\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"σύ\">σοι</span>  <span data-text=\"Χριστός\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">Χριστός</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μαρτίριος\"><span data-text=\"Μαρτίριος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Μαρτύριος\">ΜΑΡΤΙΡΙΟΣ</span></span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"εἴκοσι\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"εἴκοσι\">ΕΙΚΟΣΙ</span><span data-text=\"δύω\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"δύω\">ΔΥΩ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-text=\"εἰρήνη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"εἰρήνη\">ΕΙΡΗΝΗ</span><span data-text=\"σοι\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"σύ\">ΣΟΙ</span><span data-text=\"☧Χριστός\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">☧Σ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Dmitry Dundua, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"ζῶ\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"Μαρτίριος\" data-n=\"10\" data-lemma=\"Μαρτύριος\">ΜΑΡΤΙΡΙΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"εἴκοσι\" data-n=\"20\" data-lemma=\"εἴκοσι\">ΕΙΚΟΣΙ</span><span data-text=\"δύω\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"δύω\">ΔΥΩ</span><span data-text=\"εἰρήνη\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"εἰρήνη\">ΕΙΡΗΝΗ</span><span data-text=\"σοι\" data-n=\"35\" data-lemma=\"σύ\">ΣΟΙ</span><span data-text=\"Χριστός\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"Χριστός\">ΧΡΙΣΤΟΣ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text after De Amico and Kaibel</span>  </span>; </li><li><span>  <span>As Kaibel notes, De Amico places interpuncts between each word, but given the confusion around the numeral at the end of line 1, these seem unlikely to have been present on the original</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"1\">1: <span>Kaibel: Μαρτ[ύ]ριος; De Amico: ΕΙΚΟΣΙΑ.ΥΩ, reasonably interpreted by Kaibel as a misreading of ΔΥΩ</span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag</a></p>  <p>Martirios lived 22 years. Peace upon you. Christos</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Amico 1741 265 no.7 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186</a>  </li><li> Kirchhoff 1877 9486 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">543a</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
